org.cpsolver.studentsct.heuristics.selection

Class CriticalStandardSelection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.studentsct.heuristics.selection.StandardSelection
      • org.cpsolver.studentsct.heuristics.selection.CriticalStandardSelection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NeighbourSelection<Request,Enrollment>, AssignmentCheck<Request,Enrollment>

    public class CriticalStandardSelection
extends StandardSelection
    Use the standard IFS search for the unassigned critical course requests. This selection is based on StandardSelection using UnassignedCriticalCourseRequestSelection as variable selection. Unlike StandardSelection, it allows for a critical course request to be unassigned.
    Version:
